<D>__{i read in a book recently that killing your first man is like making love to your first woman. every smell, every nuance, you remember with a special allure, as if the acts had occured outside civilization, outside time. and when the allure is gone, you are condemned.}
<C>__{barris}
<D>__{condemned?}
